{{Infobox musical artist |name = E!E |background = group_or_band |origin = [[Příbram]], [[Czech Republic]] |instrument = Vocals, Guitar, Bass, Drums |genre = [[punk rock]] |years_active = 1987–present |website = http://www.eecka.eu }}
'''E!E''' is an important [[punk rock]] band from [[Příbram]] in the [[Czech Republic]]. It was founded in fall 1987 and it still plays today. The band members are: vocals: Bořivoj Řehoř, lead guitar and vocals: Petr Bakalerov, guitar: Petr Stawarz, bass: Petr Mottl, drums: Roman Vojtíšek.
