'''''The Boxers''''' is an outdoor 1987 steel and lacquer sculpture by [[Keith Haring]], installed in [[Berlin]], [[Germany]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://art.daimler.com/en/artwork/untitled-boxers-keith-haring-1987-2/|title=Untitled (Boxers), Keith Haring 1987 - Daimler Art Collection Daimler Art Collection|work=Daimler Art Collection}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.visitberlin.de/en/spot/the-boxers|title=Berlin -  The Boxers - visitBerlin.de EN|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://artnews.org/daimlerart/?g_cai=36868&Keith%20Haring|title=Artnews.org: Keith Haring at  Daimler Art Collection Berlin|publisher=}}</ref>

